{"tid":2231644,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–假蛋智破犯人","createTime":"2020-10-05T21:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T15:24:12.000Z","uid":38861,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e4cf627671ff8a483a4ea92b68e4d4541117dfd7","tid":2231644,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T21:00:28.000Z","msg":"違法的動物走私交易，除揚名千萬喜愛吃野味的中國之外，在世界各地亦到處發生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38GEa18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38GEa18.jpg&h=6dd0f330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以面臨頻危絕種的海龜為例，在沙灘上所誕下的海龜蛋經常成為非法之徒所偷取的目標。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）有見及此，有科學家利用3D打印技術（Ref1)，用上Ninjaflex物料模仿海龜蛋的外殼。然後再在裡頭加進GPS儀器，務求做到最終的重量及手感跟真實的海龜蛋無異。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vMvtOOQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMvtOOQ.jpg&h=cf28db38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(圖3）之後，他們分別在101個海龜蛋巢偷偷放入1隻GPS蛋。GPS蛋每一小時就會發出訊號，科學家因而亦能夠實時追蹤得到GPS蛋的去向。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cb3bMAN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCb3bMAN.jpg&h=f37c8961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）最終101隻GPS蛋裡，共有25隻被人偷走!<br />\n推算出箇中有6隻被「慣犯」發現，因而被拋置沙灘附近。<br />\n而最短的走私路線為28m附近的民居，最長的走私路線為多達137km的一帶一路。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4cOyZVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4cOyZVB.jpg&h=57a366fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果所得出的資訊，希望可以能夠為打擊走私動物方面出一分綿力。<br />\n<br />\n同時間或許亦為香港警察們帶來一個新啟示，可以嘗試在沙灘上放進海龜蛋英勇立功，而不用躊躇滿志去「為交數」而進行假掃蕩這種不堪入目的下場。<br />\n<br />\n四警涉「為交數」假掃蕩遭卧底揭發 被控串謀妨礙司法公正 押後5月再訊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%9B%9B%E8%AD%A6%E6%B6%89-%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%A4%E6%95%B8-%E5%81%87%E6%8E%83%E8%95%A9%E9%81%AD%E5%8D%A7%E5%BA%95%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%B2%E8%AC%80%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3-%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C5%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A/?fbclid=IwAR0XlJPIKO7NnIEKL-dq9nF6PYoOhMTJsZISWBPKDfgbbZiZkC-Xy9UnGOc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B6%2589-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2595%25B8-%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%258E%2583%25E8%2595%25A9%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%258D%25A7%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%25B2%25E8%25AC%2580%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E7%25A4%2599%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3-%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C5%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0XlJPIKO7NnIEKL-dq9nF6PYoOhMTJsZISWBPKDfgbbZiZkC-Xy9UnGOc&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=68610669\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B6%2589-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2595%25B8-%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%258E%2583%25E8%2595%25A9%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%258D%25A7%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%25B2%25E8%25AC%2580%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E7%25A4%2599%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3-%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C5%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0XlJPIKO7NnIEKL-dq9nF6PYoOhMTJsZISWBPKDfgbbZiZkC-Xy9UnGOc&h=8e5b0a27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%9B%9B%E8%AD%A6%E6%B6%89-%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%A4%E6%95%B8-%E5%81%87%E6%8E%83%E8%95%A9%E9%81%AD%E5%8D%A7%E5%BA%95%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%B2%E8%AC%80%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3-%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C5%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A/?fbclid=IwAR0XlJPIKO7NnIEKL-dq9nF6PYoOhMTJsZISWBPKDfgbbZiZkC-Xy9UnGOc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"red\">like</span>以及<span class=\"green\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=32610aaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=76654bd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.cell.com/current-biology/fulltext/S0960-9822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fcurrent-biology%2Ffulltext%2FS0960-9822&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=909e80ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cell.com/current-biology/fulltext/S0960-9822</a>(20)31255-0?utm_source=EA#app2"},{"pid":"8c690ca92266cf645c0bddf8798718c47c62c55a","tid":2231644,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T21:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c29cb619ba06f49566ee582eb74cf03eb7e45a7","tid":2231644,"uid":199244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T21:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688dd4cd7184e9a5cbf18fef0365c9a85